### 1. Create an Income Record
POST http://localhost:8080/api/records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 5000.00,
  "type": "INCOME",
  "category": "Salary",
  "date": "2026-04-03",
  "notes": "April Salary",
  "user": {
    "id": "60796046-0eca-483b-b1da-873cd9aefd8d"
  }
}

### 2. Create an Expense Record
POST http://localhost:8080/api/records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 150.50,
  "type": "EXPENSE",
  "category": "Groceries",
  "date": "2026-04-03",
  "notes": "Weekly groceries",
  "user": {
    "id": "60796046-0eca-483b-b1da-873cd9aefd8d"
  }
}

### 3. Get All Records For User
GET http://localhost:8080/api/records/user/60796046-0eca-483b-b1da-873cd9aefd8d

### 4. Get Dashboard Summary
GET http://localhost:8080/api/records/user/60796046-0eca-483b-b1da-873cd9aefd8d/summary